org.apache.ambari.server.state

Class ServiceLdapInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.state.ServiceLdapInfo

  • public class ServiceLdapInfo
extends Object
    ServiceLdapInfo encapsulates meta information about a service's support LDAP integration

    The data is expected to be like 

       <ldap>
     <supported>true</supported>
     <ldapEnabledTest>
         {
           "equals": [
             "service-site/ranger.authentication.method",
             "LDAP"
           ]
         }
     </ldapEnabledTest>
   </ldap>
